"I think we should repair the Ark for now. Striker's off to check out the new 
ship," he says to Shadow Wing, looking around at the Ark as Striker walks 
off. He looks back in the direction of the bridge, "The bridge was pretty 
damaged. Let's work on that first. Who contacted you?"
